# Data-Driven-Improvements-in-Education-Power-BI-Business-Intelligence

📊 Data-Driven Improvements in Education | Power BI Business Intelligence Project
📌 Project Overview

The Data-Driven Improvements in Education project is an end-to-end Business Intelligence solution developed using Microsoft Power BI to analyze educational data and support evidence-based decision-making. The objective of this project is to transform multiple educational datasets into meaningful insights that can help stakeholders understand student performance, attendance patterns, teacher effectiveness, school infrastructure, and socio-economic influences on academic outcomes.

The project demonstrates the complete Business Intelligence workflow—from raw data preparation to interactive dashboard development—using industry-standard Power BI techniques such as Power Query, Data Modeling, DAX, and Data Visualization.

🎯 Business Objective

Educational institutions and government organizations generate massive amounts of data every year. However, without proper analysis, it becomes difficult to identify performance trends and make informed decisions.

This project aims to:

Analyze student academic performance.
Evaluate attendance trends.
Study teacher qualifications and experience.
Analyze school infrastructure availability.
Understand socio-economic factors affecting education.
Build an interactive dashboard for data-driven decision-making.
