🧹 Data Cleaning & Transformation (Power Query)

The raw datasets were cleaned and transformed using Power Query Editor before loading into the Power BI data model.

Data Cleaning Activities
Imported multiple Excel datasets
Verified data types
Checked missing values
Removed duplicate records
Applied Trim & Clean transformations
Standardized categorical values
Validated relationships between datasets
Performed consistency checks
Prepared analysis-ready datasets
🏗 Data Modeling

A relational data model was created by connecting multiple tables using primary and foreign keys.

Relationships Created
Student Performance ↔ Attendance
Student Performance ↔ Socio-Economic Data
School Infrastructure ↔ Socio-Economic Data
Teacher Data ↔ School Infrastructure (State Level)

The project follows a Star Schema-inspired model to improve analytical performance and support cross-filtering between visuals.

